casebody.data:
No. 11-5312. Matthew Thomas Clarke, Petitioner v. Rick Thaler, Director, Texas Department of Criminal Justice, Correctional Institutions Division. 565 U.S. 807, 132 S. Ct. 385,

181 L. Ed. 2d 8,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6529. October 3, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 415 Fed. Appx. 529.
